com.travelbank.knit.schedulers

Interface SchedulerProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Schedulers, TestSchedulers

    public interface SchedulerProvider
    Base interface for Schedulers and it's testing counterpart. Used by InternalModels generated by the KnitProcessor. It provides instances for all schedulers available to Knit.
    See Also:
    AndroidMainThreadScheduler, ImmediateScheduler, IOScheduler, HeavyTaskScheduler
